The paper deals with the problem of image decomposition, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes a generalization of the Multicut Problem with long-range terms, which is a graph optimization problem that falls under the categories of algorithms and data structures (cs.DS), machine learning (cs.LG), graph theory (cs.GR), and computational geometry (cs.CG).
